    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Anti Inflammatory Green Smoothie"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<span><i class=\"fa fa-book\"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"/recipe-category/smoothies-and-drinks/\" rel=\"tag\">Smoothies and drinks</a></span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "April 9, 2016<span class=\"value-title\" title=\"2016-04-09\"></span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "With lots of greens and turmeric, ginger, cinnamon and black pepper this smoothie will help to reduce inflammation and pain naturally. Make double the amount and have one serving in the morning and one serving in the afternoon to spread the positive effect of anti inflammation out over your day. For the greens use any of the following: spinach, kale, silver beet, beet root leaves, carrot greens, lettuce, dandelion leaves, plantain, nettle, parsley, coriander ....)"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Prep: 5 min",
        "5 min 5 min",
        "Yields: 1-2 servings"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Ingredients"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1/2 </span> <span class=\"name\">Avocado</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1/2 cup</span> <span class=\"name\">Blueberries, frozen</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1-2 </span> <span class=\"name\">handfuls of greens</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1-2 tsp</span> <span class=\"name\">Ginger, freshly grated</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1 tsp</span> <span class=\"name\">Turmeric powder, or 1-2 cm of fresh root grated</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1/2 tsp</span> <span class=\"name\">Cinnamon (Ceylon or superior cinnamon, not cassia if possible)</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1 pinch</span> <span class=\"name\">Pepper, black, freshly ground</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">200 ml</span> <span class=\"name\">water, more or less</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "Optional"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1-3 tsp</span> <span class=\"name\">Maca root powder, start with 1 tsp and increase slowly</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1/3 </span> <span class=\"name\">Banana or a few drops of Stevia to sweeten</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1 tbsp</span> <span class=\"name\">Chia seeds, soaked</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a><span class=\"amount\">1 </span> <span class=\"name\">Lemon, juice and use juice to taste</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Directions"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "<a href=\"#\" class=\"hint-check\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"></i></a>Add all ingredients to your blender and blend on high for 30-90 seconds, depending on the power of your blender. Enjoy! Will keep in fridge for up to 8 hours."
    },
